name: Examples-for-the-web
body:
### Welcome to Examples-for-the-Web
This is currently a work in progress and is intended demonstrate various examples, samples etc on/using HTML(5) and CSS(3). This is intentionally developed for MDN Docs but I hereby allow everyone to use it for free and have a great learning :-) also if you find it useful then don't forget to drop in a mail to vikashagrawal1990@gmail.com or tweet to ivikashagrawal. I would be glad to hear from you.
 
### How to Browse
Well that wont be difficult, as examples for all the individual properties or attributes can be found in scr/ folder. Rest you will find it clean

### Authors
@ivikash

### Support or Contact
If you are facing any problems or you find bugs, please file them or notify them directly to the author.
